data.title: Enroll — Ohio Imagination Library
data.meta_description: Dolly Parton’s Imagination Library of Ohio is reaching children in all 88 counties, thanks to a network of early childhood literacy partners and generous support from the Ohio General Assembly, corporations, foundations, and individual donors.
data.text:
Thanks for joining Dolly Parton’s Imagination Library of Ohio! Enrolling is a TWO-STEP process.

If you would like to receive communications from Dolly Parton’s Imagination Library of Ohio, please complete the questions below. Click NEXT to then enroll your child in the program!

Parent Name *

County *

Parent Email Address *

Parent Cell Phone

Child Birth Month

Child Birth Year

Email Opt In

I would like to opt in to receive emails from Dolly Parton's Imagination Library of Ohio about my books and early childhood literacy. Approximately 2 emails a month.

YES

Text Opt In

I would like to receive text updates from Dolly Parton's Imagination Library of Ohio about my books and early childhood literacy. Std. msg&data rates apply. Approximately 2 msg/month.

YES

Are you enrolling your newborn baby? If so, at which hospital was your baby born?

Thank you!
